'''罗纳德·L·贝里'''（英语：Ronald L. Bailey，1956年2月- ），前[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]][[中将|中将]]，曾于2011年至2013年期间担任[[美国海军陆战队第1师|美国海军陆战队第1师]]师长，也是该师历史上首位黑人师长。<ref name=MCPR>{{cite web |url=http://www.marines.mil/unit/basecamppendleton/Pages/News/2009/CampPendletonwelcomesnewcommander.aspx |title=Camp Pendleton welcomes new commander |publisher=Marines.mil |date=2009-06-25 |accessdate=2011-09-17 |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007010940/http://www.marines.mil/unit/basecamppendleton/Pages/News/2009/CampPendletonwelcomesnewcommander.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==生平==
1956年，罗纳德·L·贝里出生于[[美国|美国]][[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[聖奧古斯丁_(佛羅里達州)|圣奥古斯丁]]。1977年，毕业于美国[[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[奥斯汀佩伊州立大学|奥斯汀佩伊州立大学]]并获得理学学士学位。随后便应征参加[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]被授予[[少尉|少尉]]军衔。在大学期间，罗纳德·L·贝里加入了[[Alpha_Phi_Alpha|Alpha Phi Alpha]]兄弟会，并且成为终身会员。在海军陆战队服役的初期，他一直担任步兵部队的基层军官。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://slsp.manpower.usmc.mil/GOSA/biographies/rptBiography.asp?PERSON_ID=196&PERSON_TYPE=General |title=Official Biography: Major General Ronald L. Bailey |publisher=Slsp.manpower.usmc.mil |date=1977-07-01 |accessdate=2011-09-17 |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318212753/https://slsp.manpower.usmc.mil/GOSA/biographies/rptBiography.asp?PERSON_ID=196&PERSON_TYPE=General |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=1st Marine Division ushers in new legacy|url=http://www.ocregister.com/news/marine-306602-bailey-general.html|publisher=The Orange County Register|accessdate=2012-05-05|author=ERIKA I. RITCHIE|date=2011-06-30|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222710/http://www.ocregister.com/news/marine-306602-bailey-general.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==服役经历==
罗纳德·L·贝里在海军陆战队服役期间历经多个单位和部门，并多次进入军事院校深造和受训。2011年1月，贝里被任命为海军陆战队征兵指挥中心（Marine Corps Recruiting Command）主管，负责海军陆战队在全美范围内的征兵、新兵训练以及培养专业教官的工作，接受其指挥的官兵多达22,000多人。<ref>{{cite web|title=MILITARY: Maj. Gen. Ronald Bailey takes command of 1st Marine Division|url=http://www.nctimes.com/news/local/article_78adce58-c129-5968-a6e0-03b4a2fd353a.html|publisher=North County Times|accessdate=2012-05-05|author=Mark Walker|date=2011-06-30|archive-date=2011-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901212604/http://www.nctimes.com/news/local/article_78adce58-c129-5968-a6e0-03b4a2fd353a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时，他还亲自坐镇美国海军陆战队[[圣地亚哥|圣地亚哥]]新兵训练中心（Marine Corps Recruit Depot San Diego）并担任总指挥。<ref name=MCPR/><ref name=CPP>{{cite web |url=http://camppendleton.patch.com/articles/first-african-american-appointed-to-command-1st-marine-division |title=First African-American Appointed to Command 1st Marine Division - Camp Pendleton, CA Patch |publisher=Camppendleton.patch.com |date=2011-07-01 |accessdate=2011-09-17 |archive-date=2012-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326110208/http://camppendleton.patch.com/articles/first-african-american-appointed-to-command-1st-marine-division |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年6月，罗纳德·L·贝里以[[少将|少将]]军衔出任[[美国海军陆战队第1师|陆战第1师]]师长，因此成为该支传奇部队有史以来第一位黑人师长。<ref name=LAT>{{cite web |author= |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/07/maj-gen-ronald-bailey-has-assumed-command-of-the-camp-pendleton-based-1st-marine-division-the-first-african-american-to-co.html |title=1st Marine Division gets first African American commander - latimes.com |publisher=Latimesblogs.latimes.com |date=2011-07-01 |accessdate=2011-09-17 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108180403/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/07/maj-gen-ronald-bailey-has-assumed-command-of-the-camp-pendleton-based-1st-marine-division-the-first-african-american-to-co.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年6月，罗纳德·L·贝里晋升为[[中将|中将]]，并被派往位于[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]的陆战队总部出任政策·策划·行动部（Plans, Policies, and Operations）副总指挥。<ref name=deen>{{cite web |url=http://www.blackengineer.com/news/the-few-the-proud-the-marines/ |title=The Few. The Proud. The Marines. |last=Deen |first=Lango |date=2017-11-06 |website=US Black Engineer News |publisher=Career Communications Group, Inc. |access-date=2018-01-07 |quote= |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127112710/https://www.blackengineer.com/news/the-few-the-proud-the-marines/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在此期间，他还曾接受[[范德堡大学|范德堡大学]]（University of Vanderbilt）的采访并阐述自己对[[管理学|管理学]]的见解。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dST93WzyiBQ|title=A conversation with Lieutenant General Ronald L. Bailey|website=YouTube.com|publisher=Vanderbilt Owen Graduate School of Management|date=2016-11-09|accessdate=2020-08-18|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816060338/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dST93WzyiBQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年7月31日，罗纳德·L·贝里在服役41年后从海军陆战队光荣退役。<ref name=deen/>

==退役后==
回归平民生活后，罗纳德·L·贝里接受了来自母校的邀请，出任[[奥斯汀佩伊州立大学|奥斯汀佩伊州立大学]]对外联络办公室副主任。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.apsu.edu/external-affairs/staff.php|title=External Affairs Staff|website=www.apsu.edu|publisher=Austin Peay State University|date=|accessdate=2020-08-18|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031221853/https://apsu.edu/external-affairs/staff.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2020年8月，贝里出任美国国家电力承包商协会（National Electrical Contractors Association，简称：NECA）工业发展部（Industry Development）副主席。<ref name="prnews">{{cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/neca-names-lt-gen-ronald-l-bailey-usmc-ret-as-vice-president-of-industry-development-301107824.html|title=NECA Names Lt. Gen. Ronald L. Bailey, USMC (Ret.), As Vice President Of Industry Development|website=prnewswire.com|date=2020-08-06|accessdate=2020-08-18|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125102543/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/neca-names-lt-gen-ronald-l-bailey-usmc-ret-as-vice-president-of-industry-development-301107824.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

